N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 210.10 - Tickets for employees and participants

State Regulations

Distribution of employees' and participants' tickets shall be
limited strictly to persons in these classifications, and such tickets shall
not be transferable. Notes
